fts along at dusk, perfectly silent. Its transient, melancholy aspect touches some people deeply\u2014every so often, one will come upon a song or poem devoted to Drifblim."}, {"version": "moon", "text": "Even while under careful observation, large flocks of Drifblim flying at dusk will inexplicably disappear from view."}, {"version": "omega-ruby", "text": "It carries people and Pok\u00e9mon when it flies. But since it only drifts, it can end up anywhere."}, {"version": "pearl", "text": "It carries people and Pok\u00e9mon when it flies. But since it only drifts, it can end up anywhere."}, {"version": "platinum", "text": "At dusk, swarms of them are carried aloft on winds. When noticed, they suddenly vanish."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "It grabs people and Pok\u00e9mon and carries them off somewhere. Where do they go? Nobody knows."}, {"version": "soulsilver", "text": "It can generate and release gas within its body. That\u2019s how it can control the altitude of its drift."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "There was once an incident in which a man took a trip riding a Drifblim, only to go missing."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "Some say this Pok\u00e9mon is a collection of souls burdened with regrets, silently drifting through the dusk."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "The raw material for the gas inside its body is souls. When its body starts to deflate, it\u2019s thought to carry away people and Pok\u00e9mon."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "There\u2019s a rumor that if you catch a Drifblim floating on the wind at dusk, you\u2019ll be carried away to the afterlife."}, {"version": "white", "text": "At dusk, swarms of them are carried aloft on winds. When noticed, they suddenly vanish."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "They carry people and Pok\u00e9mon, but the wind can catch them, so there can\u2019t be a fixed destination."}, {"version": "x", "text": "It carries people and Pok\u00e9mon when it flies. But since it only drifts, it can end up anywhere.